Package: Escort
Type: Package
Title: Escort: Data-driven Selection of Trajectory
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("Xiaoru", "Dong", , "xdong1@ufl.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-3039-3004")), 
             person(given = "Rhonda", family = "Bacher", email = "rbacher@ufl.edu", role = c("ctb", "fnd"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5787-476X")))
Description: A data-driven evaluation framework for trajectory inference. 
    Escort simplifies trajectory analysis using a three-step approach to guide users through 
    the analysis by providing goodness of fit evaluations.
